<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; line-height: 24px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; color: #1c3f94;">Dear Homeowner,</p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left;">Do you open your electricity bill each month and cringe? Your warranty from Home Warranty of America is providing you peace of mind from the unexpected surprises of owning your new home, but how to do protect yourself from that shock when you open your electricity bill? Direct Energy Solar, part of our family of brands, has the answer.</p>
<div style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 5px;"><img src="http://pages.directenergysolar.com/rs/410-XAV-850/images/Customer_Collage.jpg" alt="Direct Energy Solar Customers" height="147" width="634" /></div>
<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; line-height: 24px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 25px; padding-bottom: 0px; color: #1c3f94;">What if we told you solar energy can help you save?</p>
</div>
<p style="color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left;">In fact, solar energy has the potential to save you thousands on your energy bills for decades. That&rsquo;s money you could be pouring into your new home in other ways, like home improvements, new furniture or upgraded appliances. It&rsquo;s your money. Spend it the way you want, not the way your utility company wants.</p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: left;">Direct Energy Solar has already helped thousands of customers harness rays of sunshine to provide a consistent, reliable source of power&mdash;and they are in your neighborhood and ready to do the same for you.</p>
<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; line-height: 24px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 25px; padding-bottom: 0px; color: #1c3f94;">What are the benefits of switching to solar power?</p>
